- [F-005-03] ADOPT contract-first ordering: Spec-kit’s Iron Law verifies before completion, but Gem Team adds the earlier constraint that contract tests exist before implementation starts. [SOURCE: specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/gem-team-main/AGENTS.md:69] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-code/SKILL.md:140]
